    <abstract>
      <t>This document defines a data model for Access Control List (ACL).
   ACL is a ordered-by-user set of rules, used to configure the
   forwarding behavior in device.  Each rule is used to find a match on
   a packet, and define actions that will be performed on the packet.</t>
